Universal wiki converter framework.

The general idea is that you plug any input and any output and run it and they communicate through well known events (wiki, page, attachment, etc.).

This covers many uses cases:
* import and convert some wiki into an XWiki database (some wiki format input and XWiki database ouput)
* import a XAR (XAR input and XWiki database output)
* export a XAR (XWiki database input and XAR output)
* export to some other wiki format (XWiki databse input and some wiki format output)
* export an online wiki to a XAR trough REST (XWiki REST input and XAR output)
* ...